Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.93,0:00:03.19,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Thirty years ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.73,0:00:06.44,Character Card,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,0)}Shoudou Kurumi (39)\NHead of the Shoudou Family
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.27,0:00:06.44,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Shoudou Kurumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} befriended a boy by the sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.94,0:00:11.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ultimately, that boy saved her life in a traffic incident.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.65,0:00:15.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When Kurumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} won 100 million yen on a chance lottery ticket...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.16,0:00:18.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She decided to give it to that boy instead...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.33,0:00:20.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And announced it in magazines and on TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.33,0:00:23.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The clues were: Her memories of those summer days...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.25,0:00:27.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As well as the large scar the boy received while rescuing her.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.88,0:00:31.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Two men came forward claiming to be the boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.67,0:00:34.59,Character Card,,0,0,0,,{\fad(210,210)}Kusumoto Ryuuhei (42)
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.30,0:00:34.47,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Kusumoto Ryuuhei{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} had a scar on his back...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.13,0:00:37.01,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,While Banba Sougo{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s was on his chest.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.01,0:00:39.89,Character Card,,0,0,0,,{\fad(210,210)}Banba Sougo (41)
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.05,0:00:39.39,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Both were shaped like the number 1.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.64,0:00:43.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In order to ascertain which was truly the one...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.31,0:00:45.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We decided to go along to the Shoudou estate.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.02,0:00:46.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But there...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.02,0:00:50.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Outside that very house, investigating a\Nserial murderer from many years ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.23,0:00:53.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Were detectives from the first division, watching secretly.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.99,0:00:57.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The criminal from that time also has a 1-shaped scar on his body.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.03,0:01:01.49,Character Card,,0,0,0,,{\fad(210,0)}Houya Taisuke (40)\NButler
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.74,0:00:59.49,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.49,0:01:04.58,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,It was soon discovered that the butler of the estate,\NHouya Taisuke{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, also has a scar on his back.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.29,0:01:09.13,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Of them, which is truly the "Boy of Memory"?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.05,0:01:13.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Love is eternal, labyrinths are mysterious.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.09,0:01:14.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Saturday nights are for mystery!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.47,0:01:17.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,With the deadline approaching, it's time to identify the first love!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.47,0:01:19.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The scar case takes an unexpected turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.10,0:01:21.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Perceiving the one and only truth...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.60,0:01:23.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The appearance of a child and the intellect of an adult...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.47,0:01:25.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His name is: Detective Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.00,0:03:14.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.17,0:03:17.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's a scar on the butler's back as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.21,0:03:18.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.47,0:03:21.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Compared to those of Kusumoto{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} and Banba{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.88,0:03:24.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's short and only about 15 cm in length.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.60,0:03:30.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This also suggests that the butler,\NHouya{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, could be the serial murderer.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.56,0:03:32.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.65,0:03:35.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wasn't the serial killer's scar a big one?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.69,0:03:41.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, the superintendent couldn't exactly see well\Nat the time, after just being injured by the culprit.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.57,0:03:46.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He wasn't in a position to accurately estimate the length of the scar.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.74,0:03:51.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not to mention, it seems the murderer is quite a cautious person.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.92,0:03:57.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After the superintendent cut him,\Nthe culprit did escape by car, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.13,0:04:03.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When the police discovered the car later, there\Nwere absolutely no signs of fingerprints or blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.59,0:04:08.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since the driver's side seat cover had been peeled off...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.06,0:04:10.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His blood had probably gotten on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.93,0:04:13.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why he must have wiped away the fingerprints afterwards.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.60,0:04:18.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, why are you already suspecting the butler is the murderer?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.94,0:04:25.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If someone were that cautious, it isn't like they could\Nbe lured in with money—even if the scars were similar.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.20,0:04:34.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even though they could tell the blood had been wiped\Naway, there was no reaction at all from luminol testing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.79,0:04:36.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Those three scars...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.13,0:04:39.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kusumoto{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s is on his back.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.38,0:04:42.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Banba{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} has one on his chest.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.97,0:04:45.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, there's the small one on Houya{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s back.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.76,0:04:47.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As children...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.85,0:04:51.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kusomoto{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} was thin, and Banba{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} loved to study.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.73,0:04:55.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The boy of memory was familiar with both the sea and fish...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.15,0:04:58.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His favorite drink was ginger ale.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.98,0:05:01.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He loved to eat sushi and fried noodles...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.23,0:05:04.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As for his character, he was honest.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.61,0:05:07.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He was known to his classmates as...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.74,0:05:08.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Gari?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.16,0:05:11.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.66,0:05:14.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How is it going?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.96,0:05:15.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The investigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.37,0:05:17.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, no...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.88,0:05:19.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm not quite sure yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.13,0:05:21.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.50,0:05:23.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, there is still time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.38,0:05:26.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A midnight snack has been prepared, so, should you like...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.63,0:05:28.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Midnight snack?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.26,0:05:30.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could that be...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.43,0:05:33.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sushi maybe?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.81,0:05:34.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.02,0:05:36.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's impressive, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.98,0:05:38.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, how about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.10,0:05:40.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is a secret, though, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.90,0:05:43.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A little lower.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.53,0:05:50.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's he saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.83,0:05:55.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, I can count on you for the rest?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.41,0:05:58.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, I'm surprised...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.00,0:06:06.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was under the impression you were a short\Nhigh schooler whose voice hadn't changed yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.59,0:06:09.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But to think you're just a little boy...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.10,0:06:14.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's as if Sherlock Holmes were imitating a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.93,0:06:16.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.68,0:06:20.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm able to see that which others cannot.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.56,0:06:23.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, I'll be waiting in my room.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.53,0:06:26.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll leave the rest to you...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.95,0:06:29.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mr. Detective.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.78,0:06:31.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.79,0:06:38.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As delicious as expected!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.88,0:06:44.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mr. Butler, do you want to join us?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.92,0:06:47.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That lady said you should eat, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.76,0:06:50.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.93,0:07:00.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Natural ingredients really do taste the best.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.56,0:07:03.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, this is manufactured.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.77,0:07:05.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What're you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.32,0:07:07.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course it's natural!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.19,0:07:09.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You agree with me, don't you, Detective?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.82,0:07:10.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.28,0:07:12.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you ask me...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.91,0:07:16.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.49,0:07:20.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're wondering whether it's natural or manufactured?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.79,0:07:22.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That doesn't matter!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.13,0:07:24.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Doesn't matter"?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.00,0:07:26.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, I'd say it's important...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.92,0:07:29.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now, now—you see, the boy of memory...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.30,0:07:34.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's been said he knew the sea and fish well, and loved sushi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.47,0:07:37.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why you thought you could appeal to me with this, no?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.10,0:07:38.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.10,0:07:40.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, it wouldn't be impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.81,0:07:43.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That 100 million yen would be enticing enough to try anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.48,0:07:45.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Speaking of sushi...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.90,0:07:49.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What happened when the boy bought the packed sushi?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.11,0:07:53.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I received 100 yen in excess change,\Nso I went back to the shop to return it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.57,0:07:57.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's in my nature to not keep what isn't mine, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.41,0:08:00.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's pretty strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.21,0:08:01.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.21,0:08:07.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, that honest boy that returns\Neverything that doesn't belong to him...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.63,0:08:10.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If the chance arose for him to get\N100 million yen from someone else...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.80,0:08:13.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you think he'd take it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.39,0:08:16.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What're you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.47,0:08:23.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was all because of the help I gave her after\Nwhat happened in that accident back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.69,0:08:26.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She wanted to express her appreciation with the 100 million yen!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.86,0:08:29.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's wrong with coming and accepting it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.57,0:08:31.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You saw it yourself in the bath, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.99,0:08:34.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The big scar I got from that accident!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.66,0:08:35.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.45,0:08:39.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I owe the scar on my back to that accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.29,0:08:44.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's true that you both have large scars of around 30 cm in length.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.46,0:08:49.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, what brings questions of doubt to my mind is exactly that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.88,0:08:54.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Didn't the lady say it in the interview?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.80,0:08:57.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"The scar reached from one side to the other," were her words.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.89,0:09:02.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She didn't say much else, but she was certain it was a big scar.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.68,0:09:06.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And, about how old were you at the time?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.31,0:09:09.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was in around my second or third year of school...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.32,0:09:11.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.36,0:09:13.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you were in your second or third year at the time...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.82,0:09:17.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The scar would have only been around 15 cm long.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.07,0:09:20.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, see...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.24,0:09:23.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When I first got the scar, it was about that size.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.29,0:09:27.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As I grew up, the scar got bigger as I did...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.08,0:09:29.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.33,0:09:30.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You didn't know?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.80,0:09:34.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That scar wouldn't increase in size no matter how much you grew.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.05,0:09:36.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What!?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.18,0:09:40.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If a scar is 15 cm at the time...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.01,0:09:42.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It should stay 15 cm until death.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.31,0:09:43.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.52,0:09:45.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I just had a big physique is all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.98,0:09:47.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Same with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.44,0:09:49.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, Kusumoto{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.40,0:09:53.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I recall you mentioning being thin in your childhood.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.86,0:09:55.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.32,0:10:02.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I bet that, when you heard the boy of memory's\Nname was Gari, you mistook what it meant.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.91,0:10:04.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You took it as garigari, for "skin and bones."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.37,0:10:09.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Gari is actually for gariben, "someone who studies hard."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.75,0:10:12.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Gari from gariben, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.38,0:10:14.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.76,0:10:19.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When the boy from her memories ate fried noodles by the sea...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.76,0:10:22.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He heaped a pile of red ginger on top of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.06,0:10:24.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.77,0:10:26.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've never heard that before!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.14,0:10:29.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It should come as no surprise that you haven't.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.81,0:10:33.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is a new story that she only just told me today.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.11,0:10:36.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You still don't see it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.69,0:10:40.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The boy of memory that loved ginger ale...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.37,0:10:43.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Bought packed sushi often...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.12,0:10:46.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And heaped red ginger on his fried noodles...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.29,0:10:48.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.41,0:10:50.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That boy liked ginger, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.50,0:10:54.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ginger is one of the key ingredients in ginger ale...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.34,0:10:58.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And the Gari that goes with sushi is pickled\Nginger that results from soaking it in vinegar!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.38,0:11:02.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, does that mean that boy got the Gari from...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.18,0:11:03.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.76,0:11:07.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The boy with a fondness for ginger was known as Gari.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.77,0:11:08.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.43,0:11:11.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The one who didn't eye any other sushi...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.94,0:11:13.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But went straight for the ginger...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.23,0:11:16.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The butler, Houya Taisuke{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.69,0:11:19.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.74,0:11:21.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The real guy was here!?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.70,0:11:22.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.86,0:11:26.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's a scar on his back about 15 cm in length.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.74,0:11:28.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm not mistaken, am I!?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.16,0:11:31.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, why didn't you say something!?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.79,0:11:33.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You could have got 100 million!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.29,0:11:37.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That money is something I could never accept.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.55,0:11:42.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If I had not told her, "Stay here," back then...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.01,0:11:45.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She wouldn't have been involved in that accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.97,0:11:50.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Therefore, I decided to support in secret...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.35,0:11:53.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, it seems you weren't able to do it in secret, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.65,0:11:55.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't you see?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.52,0:12:01.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Given that she clearly knew you wouldn't\Naccept something that wasn't your own...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.70,0:12:06.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't it obvious as to why she announced\Nshe'd give you 100 million on TV?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.83,0:12:12.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She wanted the one by her side to come out and tell her.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.83,0:12:17.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She wanted you to tell her before any impersonators appeared!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.21,0:12:21.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, that lady really did already...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.76,0:12:23.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, she'd already discovered it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.09,0:12:28.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She knew that the butler, Houya{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, was the boy from her memory.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.06,0:12:33.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The reason she had you see to my back in the\Nbath, even with the broken air conditioning...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.81,0:12:36.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And her reason for withholding the red ginger story...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.40,0:12:39.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As well as why she had sushi prepared for a midnight snack...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.94,0:12:42.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They were all just hints for me to follow.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.15,0:12:43.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.90,0:12:45.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What will you do now, Houya{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.32,0:12:48.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The lady is waiting in her room.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.66,0:12:53.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.54,0:12:54.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.71,0:12:55.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.54,0:12:57.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's all right!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.50,0:13:01.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll go tell her in your place if you want!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.01,0:13:05.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Or would you like for me to tell her?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.38,0:13:11.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I know she wouldn't want these two that came\Njust for the money to use her precious memory.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.85,0:13:14.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.81,0:13:15.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I understand!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.14,0:13:17.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll tell her myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.45,0:13:28.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Seems we were able to push him well, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.41,0:13:29.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.99,0:13:30.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Geez...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.37,0:13:35.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,With my situation as it is, I couldn't tell the truth even if I wanted...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.29,0:13:37.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Were you saying something?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.38,0:13:41.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's Kamen Yaiba!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.38,0:13:44.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It'd be terrible if his identity were revealed!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.26,0:13:47.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, I'll just...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.05,0:13:49.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You know...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.76,0:13:54.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please wait just a moment longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.18,0:13:56.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The police?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.89,0:13:58.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We were just joking!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.48,0:14:01.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I got this scar on my chest while surfing a long time ago, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.86,0:14:02.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.94,0:14:06.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Our business is with the one with the big scar on his back...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.32,0:14:08.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.61,0:14:10.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As for that scar...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.53,0:14:14.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Some twenty years ago, there was a serial killer...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.29,0:14:17.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who, after being cornered by Superintendent Matsumoto...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.96,0:14:21.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ended up with a 1-shaped scar on his back from a katana.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.96,0:14:26.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I couldn't remember whether it was on the back or the front at first.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.34,0:14:29.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, with the mail from Mouri, it all became clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.93,0:14:31.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mail?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.85,0:14:33.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, man...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.31,0:14:35.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I forgot to return Uncle's phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.93,0:14:40.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Normally, when someone is injured,\Nthey'll cover the wound with their hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.44,0:14:47.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,However, there was no reaction on the steering\Nwheel when we tried the luminol test, because...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.99,0:14:50.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His hand couldn't reach the wound.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.70,0:14:54.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In other words, it was on his back.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.49,0:15:01.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You pulled off the cover on the driver's\Nseat to get rid of the blood, did you not?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.71,0:15:03.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.88,0:15:04.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's not it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.71,0:15:08.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I met a guy a long time ago that had a scar\Non his back, and I thought it was cool...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.13,0:15:10.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, I just copied him!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.84,0:15:12.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Enough with the random excuses!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.51,0:15:14.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's true!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.68,0:15:15.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please, believe me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.10,0:15:18.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And, did this man happen to be whistling?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.73,0:15:20.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did he?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.19,0:15:21.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.98,0:15:24.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I think it was...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.52,0:15:27.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A song that was popular like, twenty years ago!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.40,0:15:28.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is this the truth?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.40,0:15:30.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.70,0:15:31.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Superintendent...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.11,0:15:35.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A song that was popular twenty years ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.66,0:15:37.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The song of the serial killer...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.21,0:15:49.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His name is Kusumoto Ryuuhei, 42 years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.51,0:15:55.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The incident dates back to fifteen years\Nago, when he was homestaying abroad.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.85,0:15:57.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We were able to verify it, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.81,0:15:59.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He can be removed from the list of possible suspects.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.43,0:16:01.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.52,0:16:08.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He came across the man in question at a\Nsauna, just before leaving for his homestay.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.11,0:16:13.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There was a towel covering his face, so he wasn't entirely visible.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.32,0:16:18.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"The scar on my back is a badge of courage\Na cop gave me some five years back."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.03,0:16:19.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"You want one too, by any chance?"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.49,0:16:22.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's what he said, with a laugh.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.50,0:16:23.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And that sauna?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.17,0:16:27.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sato and Takagi have just gone to make inquiries.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.13,0:16:30.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tell them to be on their guard.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.88,0:16:31.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.30,0:16:34.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Two victims twenty years ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.01,0:16:35.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,One victim fifteen years ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.80,0:16:37.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's three victims he's claimed...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.72,0:16:38.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's a ruthless criminal.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.47,0:16:41.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, there's one more.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.73,0:16:43.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Have you forgotten?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.44,0:16:46.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How could I forget?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.86,0:16:51.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Superintendent Morimura, who was\Nkilled in the line of the duty on that case.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.49,0:16:56.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He was the man who taught me the\Nfundamentals of being a police officer.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.87,0:17:06.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Superintendent Morimura...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.08,0:17:12.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even after being promoted two classes\Nahead after you died in the line of duty...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.55,0:17:15.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I still don't understand...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.55,0:17:17.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What you meant back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.64,0:17:20.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Matsumoto...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.31,0:17:22.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's something...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.31,0:17:25.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His whistling...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.81,0:17:29.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's definitely something to it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.11,0:17:35.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just what did you mean, Morimura?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.74,0:17:40.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And we ended up with nothing for our effort.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.62,0:17:42.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's nothing that can be done.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.49,0:17:44.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The case was fifteen years ago, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.04,0:17:46.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.08,0:17:50.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The building's been renovated, and\Nthe class of customers have changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.13,0:17:55.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, there's a large remodeled spa on 5th\Nstreet that everyone is saying is great!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.92,0:17:56.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Really now?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.97,0:18:00.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why don't you head over there with Chiba{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.26,0:18:03.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'd rather go alone...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.64,0:18:05.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.18,0:18:06.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Were you inviting me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.81,0:18:08.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course I was!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.31,0:18:10.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, how about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.31,0:18:14.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If we catch the serial killer before the deadline...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.73,0:18:15.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The two of us will go to the hot spring.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.24,0:18:18.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, there's only three days...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.57,0:18:21.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Take me to the hot spring!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.03,0:18:23.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.12,0:18:24.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is this really all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.66,0:18:28.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Police officers being so lovey-dovey while on duty.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.04,0:18:31.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We weren't being lovey-dovey...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.09,0:18:34.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We're here asking about...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.34,0:18:37.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't reveal too much to the children!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.47,0:18:39.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're right...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.55,0:18:40.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.59,0:18:43.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To summarize the case from what's been on TV...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.18,0:18:46.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Along with the story I heard from Superintendent Matsumoto...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.10,0:18:48.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The first case occurred twenty years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.81,0:18:53.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The victim was a 50 year-old doctor: Boukawa Tsuguharu{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.77,0:18:56.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The murder weapon was the Japanese sword from his house.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.74,0:18:59.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just two days later, the next victim was...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.95,0:19:02.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,An associate professor of science and engineering at Tohto University...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.53,0:19:04.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The 42 year-old Mugita Atsunori{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.99,0:19:06.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The weapon was the same sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.16,0:19:09.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, while a detective was questioning him...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.96,0:19:13.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There was a driver that appeared suspicious\Nthat ended up suddenly driving off.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.00,0:19:17.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The detective on duty was struck by the car, and died.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.92,0:19:22.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After he caught up with the car, Superintendent\NMatsumoto was attacked by the culprit...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.59,0:19:24.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And even though his left eye was injured...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.47,0:19:27.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He took the katana from his attacker and cut him across his back.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.60,0:19:30.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As a result, a 1-shaped scar was left behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.19,0:19:32.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And five years later...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.10,0:19:37.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nabei Susumu{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, a 34 year-old lawyer, was\Nkilled with a kitchen knife from his own home.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.65,0:19:39.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His method.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.74,0:19:41.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Render them unconscious with a stun gun...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.95,0:19:45.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And then cruelly slice at their bodies with swords and bladed weapons.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.28,0:19:50.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In all three home cases, there were no signs of break-ins...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.29,0:19:53.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Which led police to believe it was an acquaintance, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.71,0:19:57.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The case went cold because no common points\Ncould be found to connect the three victims.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.34,0:19:59.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, I'm right, aren't!?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.51,0:20:00.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.38,0:20:03.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, I still don't get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.72,0:20:09.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The first and second victims died by the same weapon,\Nwhich is why it's assumed they share a perpetrator, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.10,0:20:09.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.31,0:20:12.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The case five years later involved a kitchen knife.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.19,0:20:15.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How do you know it was the same offender?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.73,0:20:17.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, no, that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.02,0:20:17.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's because...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.15,0:20:19.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All of the victims had the same letter cut into...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.69,0:20:21.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait, Sato{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.74,0:20:24.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Weren't you the one who told me to stay quiet about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.82,0:20:25.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.95,0:20:27.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Every time these kids ask...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.74,0:20:33.29,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,With under three days remaining before the\Ndeadline is upon us, do you think he can caught?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.16,0:20:31.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They're broadcasting about it now!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.33,0:20:32.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That case!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.58,0:20:35.54,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Criminal Psychologist, Hiramune{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.67,0:20:39.84,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,With the conditions as they are, let's say that it's highly unlikely.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.13,0:20:43.38,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,The culprit has probably drawn the curtains...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.30,0:20:46.39,Character Card,,0,0,0,,{\fad(210,0)}Hiramune Douji (41)\NCriminal Psychologist
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.47,0:20:44.72,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Unplugged his phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.76,0:20:46.39,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,And isolated himself from the outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.68,0:20:51.56,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,The suspect is likely trembling in bed,\Nwaiting for the deadline to pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.98,0:20:55.14,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,To remain inconspicuous, he'll keep disposing of his safe tiles...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.19,0:20:57.15,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Just waiting for this round to end.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.44,0:21:00.65,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,In the event that isn't the case, come kill me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.94,0:21:06.66,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,If you're prepared to throw away the hardships you've\Nendured while hiding for fifteen years, I mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.41,0:21:08.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I know that man!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.16,0:21:12.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He lives in the same apartment building as I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.25,0:21:15.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, since we're going over to Ayumi's to play today...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.71,0:21:17.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We might get to see him, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.54,0:21:18.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That man there.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.84,0:21:19.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Perhaps.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.46,0:21:22.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.05,0:21:25.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We might come across the serial killer as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.68,0:21:26.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.80,0:21:27.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't come!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.09,0:21:30.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ai{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}, you're scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.68,0:21:33.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, have a safe walk home.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.39,0:21:36.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't hesitate to call us if the murderer appears!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.44,0:21:37.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.48,0:21:42.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A letter on the bodies of the victims, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.36,0:21:47.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.57,0:21:50.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You can totally see the buildings way out there!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.49,0:21:53.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The scenery at night must be really great, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.16,0:21:54.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We're home!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.87,0:21:57.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We bought juice!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.87,0:21:59.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And quite a few snacks as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.25,0:22:03.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You bought Yaiba chocolate too?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.05,0:22:03.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.21,0:22:05.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,By the way...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.30,0:22:08.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We happened to pass a strange man near the entrance.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.47,0:22:09.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A strange man?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.30,0:22:14.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was a man who was whistling and wearing an off-season long coat.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.64,0:22:17.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What!?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.10,0:22:19.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What kind of person was this!?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.77,0:22:20.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did you see his face!?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.40,0:22:22.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.19,0:22:24.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He had a beard, and a hat drawn over his face...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.03,0:22:26.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Listen, all of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.07,0:22:28.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Until I get back, don't take a single step out of this room!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.49,0:22:34.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is it possible that guy heard Hiramune{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} speaking on TV...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.58,0:22:35.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And really came after him!?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.37,0:22:38.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The serial killer!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.62,0:24:02.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hiramune{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.29,0:24:06.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The suspect was whistling at the time...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.17,0:24:09.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,While tears poured down his face.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.15,0:24:32.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Next Conan's Hint
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.07,0:24:35.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Letter Z
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.11,0:24:36.74,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,I'll protect you, Ayumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.74,0:24:38.74,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Oh? And what about me?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.74,0:24:42.75,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,What now, Mitsuhiko?
